    section.for-attendees
      .container
        h3 For Attendees

        h5 Already know you're coming? #[a.alt(style="padding: 0; font-size: inherit;", href="http://nashvillecivichackday.eventbrite.com", target="_blank") Register on our Eventbrite page.]

        h5 Join our mailing list to get news and updates

